{"tid":1407022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"萬人讚頌黃大仙!!!","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T14:40:23.000Z","uid":217688,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"567298a12e1d5b37d27c816752b51a173a17dc6c","tid":1407022,"uid":217688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"話說6月中個陣 一眾基督教徒帶領大家唱&quot;Sing Hallelujah to the Lord&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨化黑警 為香港未來祈禱<br />\n有見及此 我哋不妨喺聽日黃大仙嘅三罷集會入面讚頌大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬人齊唱黃大仙頌 為香港集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃大仙頌:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xU5zFqo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxU5zFqo.jpg&h=759dc4cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nMusic: <a href=\"http://www.holap.org.hk/song.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.holap.org.hk%2Fsong.html&d=wovbC19maxltJNBkbBY4lJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=c4a8965e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.holap.org.hk/song.html</a><br />\n<br />\n再加上立場姐姐所寫嘅黃大仙頌空耳版:<br />\n<strong>戴哉汪鱔 欣跡赤衝 叱sad顯遠鳳<br />\n蚊西翳未 溫樣到宗 現燈夫開種<br />\n戴似帶冤制翻用 狗冇娘 (老土嗰個「娘」)關通<br />\n欲彩興學 刀至種翁 二精羊通蒙<br />\n踭花郁 魚天（陰上聲）通 一hey偏太哄<br />\n威拎軒 人澤窿 蠻放muk (muk嘴個muk) 星貢！</strong><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156064836417827&amp;set=a.10150108445227827&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156064836417827%26set%3Da.10150108445227827%26type%3D3%26theater&d=wovbC19maxltJNBkbBY4lJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=56a58685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156064836417827&amp;set=a.10150108445227827&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n大家可以先喺屋企跟住音樂試唱一次 然後我哋聽日一齊唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528843199a0aa5434d5d91e6eb6cfa042e765f67","tid":1407022,"uid":217688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:39:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c90652de7798f8a7d6141683850c8e6faa70920b","tid":1407022,"uid":217688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1d96b0e363f294201e86ddb2f4cf740234c27a","tid":1407022,"uid":217688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:39:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f955349abdc505e0fd747ace94ecf998ad07082","tid":1407022,"uid":217688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8d589a68cff5da6e36fb6ba4bc077efb4a44ad","tid":1407022,"uid":217688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421ba83ec97c0ec904a161a53b5522625a85102e","tid":1407022,"uid":217688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:39:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b641ef7a39658e7577051f521a33f1c08133a4c","tid":1407022,"uid":217688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d711a7c974b4b871eccce603a5c12518fd43e79a","tid":1407022,"uid":217688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648ebcc87066d9b3c9eff38b831cc41649e48544",